features: Fashionable & durable stitched quilted polyester fabric. The queensbury 4 Piece Set Consists of a 20" Expandable spinner carry-on, 24" Expandable spinner, 28" Expandable spinner and 15" Vertical under the seat bag. Spinners have aluminum channel tubes for added strength and ergonomic comfort grip locking trolley handle.

Spinners have 8-low profile 360 degree multi-directional wheels mounted to grid base for stability. Convenient top, side & button carry handles. Full London Fog signature lining. Interior has a zippered mesh pocket & tie down straps. Expand 2.5" For additional packing capacity. Industrial self repairing nylon zippers, protective corner guards & rear ID pocket slot and front exterior pocket for last minute items.

The vertical under the seat bag is designed to comfortably fit underneath most standard airline seats. Versatile case can be used as a rolling tote, business case or as an Overnighter. Fully lined interior has multiple zippered storage compartments.

Under seat bag has aluminum locking push button handle system with channels for added strength and in-line skate wheels provide smooth rolling. Three exterior storage pockets and rear piggyback strap makes it easy to slide over upright handle.
body.description: The London Fog 4 piece queensbury spinner set has all the pieces you need for your travels. Including a 15" Vertical under the seat bag and 20" Expandable spinner Carry-On for your shorter trips and a 24" And 28" Expandable spinner for your longer trips.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: London Fog Queensbury 4 Piece Set You will travel with confidence along with your Queensbury 4 Piece Spinner Luggage Set and feel like you're traveling first class. The London Fog Queensbury Collection gives you a classic yet stylish feel. Made of durable stitched quilted polyester material sure to withstand all your travels. This set is perfect for your short, mid or long length getaways and you will have all the pieces you need. In addition to having plenty of room for all your travel needs. The spinner uprights have 8-low profile spinner wheels. Depending on your travel needs, you can use all the bags for yourself or share the set with your family. This collection has 3 spinner sizes (20" expandable carry-on spinner, 24" expandable spinner and a 28" expandable spinner) as well as a 15" Under the Seat Bag.

London Fog Queensbury Features Piggyback feature design The back of the under the seat bag offers a design that will allow you to slide it over your upright handle for easy carrying. Recessed 8-Spinner Wheel System 8 low profile recessed spinner wheels on the 20, 24, and 28 inch bags are mounted to a grid base & positioned at the corners for superior balance & smooth rolling along with fitting today's airline standards Spacious Interior The interior is spacious and allows for ample room during your travels. There is interior shoe pockets and zippered pocket and tie down straps that help secure clothes during your travels

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great looks and very durable
reviews.reviewText: Luggage looks really expensive and we actually receive compliments from many travelers. Luggage is very durable and hold up well. This is our second set or addition to our existing set as one piece was lost. We really likeit.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2022
reviews.reviewText: We use this luggage right after I bought it and took it on our trip to Texas for 2 weeks. We basically left out of it for that time. It is a great luggage set especially for the price value. It is very durable and it's beautiful. There is so much room for all your belongings and has great compartmental space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful Queensberry set
reviews.reviewText: The set of London Fog Queensberry is beautiful! Lightly padded quilting and I bought in navy color. I only worry about the quilt stitching breaking which would be horrible.The best price was Amazon.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought this set a month ago for a trip to Europe. Over all I love the style and all the different sizes. Really happy with it.The only thing I was not really happy was that the expansion Zipper on the 24' suitcase broke with the second use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We haven’t used this yet but the set looks just like the advertisement, so far we are very pleased. Was wondering if you have a garment bag just like the set?

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Nice looking but not worth the $$$
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this on January 8, 2022. Since then I have done a bit of traveling. The handles on this set are very flimsy and they stick when you try to put them pack down. Also the wheels are not sturdy. the wheels on the large suitcase are bent after only about 3 uses. The good things I can say are the large suitcase has a ton of room. They are also very attractive and I get a ton of compliments. However, I would never purchase these again. I just purchased a set of Samsonite - spent less and got way better quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Light weight, easy to store
reviews.reviewText: I bought these for a Mediterranean crusie and they did not disappoint. They are easy to roll and very light weight. Beautiful set and easy to store.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Got this for someone who travels a lot. She has yet to put it to good use yet but the quality of these were fantastic. The only confusing thing that was more on us than anything is that the labeling makes it seem like it should be a 5 piece set when there are only four. Looks great otherwise.
Love the set!! Can’t wait to use it!!
This is a good buy. Great quality and came in good condition.

reviews.reviewTitle: Es justo el equipaje que esperaba
reviews.reviewText: Hace tiempo tenía este juego de equipaje en mi Wish List, pero no estaba disponible; tan pronto lo estuvo, lo adquirí y no me decepcionó, las maletas son funcionales y hermosas.

reviews.reviewTitle: Desirable luggage set for high flyer/traveller!
reviews.reviewText: Haven’t tried this out yet as it only arrived today ,it actually it came in good time and before the estimated arrival!!The set came stacked in each other which is good if you need to take extra cases to bring your holiday trinkets home .So my first thoughts on opening my set was nice colour nice size and nice set of luggage ,the inside liner is also very nice .Overall nice quality bags and material so if your looking for that perfect look and a classy luggage set ,this London Fog set will not disappoint!Still have to use it so can’t comment on sturdiness but I am happy with my purchase and I’m so looking forward to taking it on my vacation .
Great quality. Arrived on time and packaged intact. Can hardly wait to use.
